name: General Ledger
query:
SELECT
    `tabGL Entry`.date AS "Date:200",
    `tabGL Entry`.account AS "Account:link/Account:200",
    `tabGL Entry`.debit_amt AS "Debit:200",
    `tabGL Entry`.credit_amt AS "Credit:200",
    `tabGL Entry`.voucher_type AS "Voucher Type:200",
    `tabGL Entry`.voucher_referance AS "Voucher Reference:200",
    `tabGL Entry`.against AS "Against:200",
    `tabGL Entry`.party_type AS "Party Type:200",
    `tabGL Entry`.party AS "Party:200"
FROM
    `tabGL Entry`
